---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Resume" description="Jason Marsh — Director of Technology, 13+ years IT, assistive technology, infrastructure, and solo development.">
  <div class="resume-top">
    <h1>Resume</h1>
    <button class="resume-download" onclick="window.print()">Save as PDF</button>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <p class="resume-intro">
      Director of Technology with 13+ years of IT experience spanning infrastructure
      management, assistive technology services, and team leadership. Promoted three
      times in five years based on demonstrated results, including growing AT service
      revenue from $17K to over $200K annually. Combines hands-on technical expertise
      across Microsoft 365/Azure, Windows/Linux, and networking with an ATACP
      certification for assistive technology assessments.
    </p>

    <h2>Experience</h2>

    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-header">
        <strong>Director of Technology</strong>
        <span class="meta">May 2025 – Present</span>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-org">Lighthouse Center for Vital Living — Duluth, MN</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Lead IT and Assistive Technology divisions for a nonprofit serving people with disabilities and aging populations, overseeing infrastructure, AT services, and an AT lending library partnered with the Minnesota STAR Program</li>
        <li>One of four organizational leaders reporting to the Executive Director; contribute to strategic planning, budgeting, and cross-department decision-making</li>
        <li>Manage a team of four including an IT support specialist, an ATP, and two AT specialists; oversee hiring, training, and development</li>
        <li>Restructured AT billing operations and coached staff on proposals and invoicing, growing annual service revenue from $17K to over $200K</li>
        <li>Hold ATACP certification from CSUN; conduct AT assessments and recommend AI-powered solutions including Be My Eyes, Seeing AI, OrCam Reader, and Meta Ray-Ban smart glasses</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-header">
        <strong>IT Manager & Accessibility Specialist</strong>
        <span class="meta">Mar 2021 – May 2025</span>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-org">Lighthouse Center for Vital Living — Duluth, MN</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Assumed IT management responsibilities, conducted a full systems audit, and established thorough documentation and standardized processes organization-wide</li>
        <li>Led cloud migration from on-premises infrastructure to Microsoft 365 and Azure AD during a simultaneous building relocation, reducing annual IT costs by $15,000+</li>
        <li>Established disaster recovery procedures, security protocols, and a technology replacement plan</li>
        <li>Managed endpoints via Microsoft Intune (Windows) and IBM MaaS360 (iOS/Android) covering MDM, app deployment, and compliance</li>
        <li>Built a centralized request tracking system with Microsoft Forms and Excel to streamline IT and AT workflows</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-header">
        <strong>Accessible Technology Specialist</strong>
        <span class="meta">Oct 2020 – Mar 2021</span>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-org">Lighthouse Center for Vital Living — Duluth, MN</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Evaluated and configured assistive technology — screen readers, magnification tools, wearable devices — for clients with disabilities and aging-related needs</li>
        <li>Trained staff and clients on AT usage; attended ATIA and Closing The Gap conferences to stay current on emerging products</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-header">
        <strong>Technical Administrator</strong>
        <span class="meta">Nov 2012 – Nov 2020</span>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-org">Westside Pet Clinic — Duluth, MN</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Sole IT administrator for a veterinary practice over eight years, managing all hardware, networking, and software</li>
        <li>Led transition from paper records to electronic medical systems and developed custom internal workflows</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Independent Projects</h2>
    <p>
      I build and ship production software independently. Select projects:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/projects/mealdeck/">MealDeck</a> — meal planning app with AI-powered recipe adaptation, voice-controlled cook mode, and smart grocery grouping</li>
      <li><a href="/projects/radiogridxl/">RadioGridXL</a> — zero-dependency accessible radio streaming app, WCAG AA compliant, deployed to older adults at my organization</li>
      <li><a href="/projects/petfeedr/">PetFeedr</a> — Python-backed automated pet feeder with web interface, configurable scheduling, adjustable portions, and feed-time randomization</li>
      <li><a href="/projects/echoetcher/">EchoEtcher</a> — voice-to-structured-notes pipeline using local Whisper transcription and LLM processing</li>
      <li>AI Object Identification for the Blind (in development) — enclosed device where users place items for camera-based identification via LLM processing, reading text aloud and describing objects for users with vision loss</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Technical Skills</h2>
    <div class="resume-skills">
      <div>
        <strong>Infrastructure</strong>
        <p>Microsoft 365, Azure AD, Active Directory, Windows Server, Hyper-V, VMware/ESXi, Proxmox VE, DNS/DHCP, VPN, TCP/IP, Firewall Management</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Endpoint & Security</strong>
        <p>Microsoft Intune, IBM MaaS360, Linux Administration, Disaster Recovery, Incident Response, Access Control, Cloud Security</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Development</strong>
        <p>Python, JavaScript, Node.js, Express, PowerShell, HTML/CSS, SQL, LLM Integration & Prompt Engineering, Computer Vision APIs, Git, Arduino/ESP-8266</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Platforms</strong>
        <p>SharePoint, Microsoft Teams, ServiceNow, FreshDesk, Docker, Tailscale, GitHub Actions, Remote Desktop</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Education & Certifications</h2>
    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-header">
        <strong>Assistive Technology Applications Certificate (ATACP)</strong>
        <span class="meta">Sept 2025</span>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-org">California State University, Northridge</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-header">
        <strong>Network Administration & Cybersecurity (coursework)</strong>
        <span class="meta">2022</span>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-org">Lake Superior College</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-header">
        <strong>Full Stack Web Developer Nanodegree</strong>
        <span class="meta">June 2018</span>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-org">Udacity</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-header">
        <strong>B.S. Video Game Art & Design</strong>
        <span class="meta">Mar 2010</span>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-org">Art Institute of Pittsburgh</div>
    </div>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:regularlyjason@icloud.com">regularlyjason@icloud.com</a></li>
      <li>LinkedIn: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jason-marsh">jason-marsh</a></li>
      <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/Minimalistic">Minimalistic</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .resume-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--fg-soft);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .resume-entry {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .resume-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .resume-org {
    color: var(--fg-soft);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .resume-entry ul {
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
  }
  .resume-skills {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  .resume-skills p {
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--fg-soft);
  }
  .resume-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .resume-top h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .resume-download {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    padding: 0.45em 1.1em;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--bg-elev2);
    color: var(--fg-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .resume-download:hover {
    color: var(--leaf);
    border-color: var(--leaf);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--leaf) 8%, var(--bg-elev2));
  }


</style>

<style is:global>
  @media print {
    /* hide site chrome */
    nav.site-nav,
    footer.site-foot,
    .layout::before,
    body::after { display: none !important; }

    /* reset backgrounds */
    body, .layout {
      background: white !important;
      color: #1a1a1a !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      margin: 0 !important;
      max-width: none !important;
      font-size: 11pt !important;
    }

    .resume-top { display: block; }
    .resume-download { display: none; }

    /* add name header for PDF */
    .resume-top::before {
      content: 'Jason Marsh';
      display: block;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: 22pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.15em;
    }
    .resume-top::after {
      content: 'Duluth, MN \2022  regularlyjason@icloud.com \2022  linkedin.com/in/jason-marsh \2022  github.com/Minimalistic';
      display: block;
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 1em;
    }
    h1 { display: none; }

    h2 {
      font-size: 12pt !important;
      margin-top: 1.25rem !important;
      border-color: #ccc !important;
    }
    .resume-intro {
      font-size: 10pt !important;
      color: #333 !important;
    }
    .resume-entry { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .resume-org { font-size: 9pt !important; }
    .resume-skills { gap: 0.5rem; }
    .resume-skills p { font-size: 9pt !important; }

    a { color: #1a1a1a !important; text-decoration: none !important; }
    a::after { display: none !important; }
  }
</style>
